rows.label: bf07250100_0010
rows.name:
My Prince! Zeke! Not
like this! Not here!

rows.label: bf07250100_0020
rows.name:
Just a little more, the town is just a little
further! You have to hang in there until then.

rows.label: bf07250100_0030
rows.name:
Don't worry about me...
Go on...without me...

rows.label: bf07250100_0050
rows.name:
If you die, I'll return to my
Core Crystal again, you know.

rows.label: bf07250100_0060
rows.name: I don't want to forget everything!

rows.label: bf07250100_0080
rows.name:
I hope your next Driver will
be a bit better than me...

rows.label: bf07250100_0090
rows.name: I don't want another Driver! I want you!
